{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_011c7XoarkRAgnZgEBL1mG7A","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture:\n\nThe case has:\n- Two StatefulSets: `es-alpha` (3 nodes - the \"prod\" cluster with data) and `es-beta` (1 node - the \"dev\" cluster)\n- Services:\n  - `es-alpha` (headless) → es-alpha pods\n  - `es-beta` (headless) → es-beta pods\n  - `search-http` → **es-beta** (1 node, dev cluster) — THIS IS THE BUG, it should point to es-alpha\n  - `search-direct` → es-alpha (3 nodes, prod cluster)\n  - `search-alt` → es-beta (1 node, dev cluster)\n\nThe actual data lives in `es-alpha`, but `search-http` is wired to `es-beta`, which is why `log-reader` gets zero documents. The fix is straightforward: update `search-http`'s selector to target `es-alpha` instead. Though I'm noticing the deployed cluster only shows `es-cluster` as a single StatefulSet, not the separate `es-alpha` and `es-beta` setup described here.\n\nLooking at what's actually running versus what should be there, it seems the precondition deployed a different environment entirely—possibly from an older case like `bootstrap-initial-master-nodes` or `full-restart-upgrade-ha`. The `internal-http-service-drift` resources weren't fully applied, and the precondition log shows it was checking for 4 running pods but something went wrong partway through. I need to examine the log-reader and log-writer configurations to see what they're expecting in terms of service names and cluster setup, then decide whether to create the missing resources or adapt the existing deployment.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1625,"cache_read_input_tokens":37316,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1625},"output_tokens":19,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ede7addc-2093-4ed0-a865-42ff66fabead","uuid":"5a6aec18-e138-4a5f-a8ad-813c87797e39","request_id":"req_011CccGWZCtnR6CqjfBTGuRr"}
